Laika Actions to streamline and automate release process
This issue is duplicated by LK-2563

Have a YAML file in our backend project that the pipeline reads to execute jobs or specific Django commands.

The problem we’re trying to solve is to provide an automated way to run Django commands for feature-specific needs like migrations, data changes, etc.
